ENTRY            F1172   20260116   20260311   20260311       F107
SUBENT        F1172001   20260116   20260311   20260311       F107
BIB                  8         23
TITLE      Formation of light nuclei in reactions with 11B and
           20Ne ions at energies of 18-20 MeV per nucleon
AUTHOR     (A.V.Belozerov, K.Borcea, I.Wincour, M.Lewitowizc,
           N.H.Chau, Yu.A.Penionzhkevich, N.K.Skobelev, A.Chasha)
INSTITUTE  (4ZZZDUB)
REFERENCE  (J,BAS,52,(11),90,1988) English translation
           (J,IZV,52,2171,1988)
FACILITY   (CYCLO,4ZZZDUB) Accelerator of heavy ions
DETECTOR   (TELES,SI) Two dE-E telescopes were used. Each
           telescope consisted of a silicon dE detector with the
           thickness of sensitive layer 60 mu-m and E detector
           with a sensitive layer of 2 mm.
           (SIBAR) Detector was placed at the angle of 10 degrees
           to ion beam direction.
METHOD     (BCINT)
           (EDE)
HISTORY    (20121213C)
           (20130408A) REACTIONs codes in Sub 002-077 were
           changed, STATUS in Sub 044-047 was added.
           (20180910A) SD: DATA-ERR corrected in Subents 048-077.
           Author's names corrected according to BAS,52,(11),90.
           Small corrections in all Subents.
           (20260116U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
ENDBIB              23
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           26
